text: Yohanna is a 2024 Indonesian British Italian drama movie directed by Razka Robby Ertanto and starring Laura Basuki, Kirana Putri Grasela, Videlis Siprianus Diki, Iqua Tahlequa. ==Other websites== * Category:2024 drama movies Category:Indonesian movies Category:British drama movies Category:Italian drama movies Category:Movies about Catholicism Category:Movies set in Indonesia
